summary: Contains 4 esp files, each effecting the amount of stamina consumption from sprinting differently.
descriptionHtml:
Contains 4 esp files, each effecting the amount of stamina consumption from sprinting differently.

The esp files and there effects are as follows.

1. Extended Sprinting Duration (Slight) - Reduces the stamina consumption while sprinting slightly.

2. Extended Sprinting Duration (50%) - Reduces the stamina consumption while sprinting by half.

3. Extended Sprinting Duration (Great) - Almost completely reduces the stamina consumption while sprinting.

4. Unlimited Sprinting - Completely removes the stamina consumption while sprinting.


All files from this mod are compatible with everything.

The unlimited sprint file is also available on the steam workshop - http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=274044534&searchtext=
author: Scarynightmare
